## Get Groups

> Topic

```
Format:  lrn/hc/config
Example: lrn:luci:vn-hn:5/thing/99/hc/config
```

> Get 2 groups:

```json
{
    "cmd": "get",
    "reqid": "ios-Samsung Galaxy S10+-1565867052374-115",
    "objects": [{
        "type": "groups",
        "data": [
            "u7PqzLgeGiSUHEAeLN5snDmAxG2PRw6L",
